    <item>
      <title>欧盟企业对中国投资的兴趣降至历史最低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/eu-firms-appetite-for-china-investment-sinks-to-record-low</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国欧盟商会的一项调查显示，随着企业寻求规避地缘政治风险并转向东南亚和欧洲，中国作为最佳投资国的地位正在丧失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/eu-firms-appetite-for-china-investment-sinks-to-record-low</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 00:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>索尼计划以 13 亿美元收购 Blackstone 和 KKR 漫画应用程序</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/sony-plans-bid-versus-blackstone-kkr-for-1-3-billion-manga-app</link>
      <description><![CDATA[索尼音乐娱乐公司 (Sony Music Entertainment) 正准备对私募股权基金 Blackstone Inc. 和 KKR &amp; Inc. 发起竞购。 Co. 将收购日本电子漫画提供商 Infocom Corp.，这笔交易估计价值约 2000 亿日元（13 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/sony-plans-bid-versus-blackstone-kkr-for-1-3-billion-manga-app</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 09:48:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元的脆弱性引发了亚洲新货币战争的担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/yen-s-fragility-raises-specter-of-a-new-currency-war-in-asia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着日元跌至新低，一些投资者正在考虑在一个忙于支撑不断下跌的汇率的地区几乎不可想象的情况——一系列竞争性贬值引发了新的亚洲货币战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/yen-s-fragility-raises-specter-of-a-new-currency-war-in-asia</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 21:25:01 GMT</pubDate>
